main event: Natives of Crete reported a disk-shaped object observed on 17 March 1949.
interesting points: The object was described as the size of a bicycle wheel., The color of the object was noted as white., The object flew at an altitude of 1,000 meters and moved from northeast to southwest., Witnesses reported buzzing sounds coming from various directions., The sightings of disk-shaped objects had previously been prominent in the US in 1947.
